name: Field #001
description:
A strange field object. It's shape changes according to a variable alpha (values between 1.2 and 1.55) and a variable beta (values between 0.6 and 1.5). Observe and find out what it is like!
Controls: 
- set the value of variable alpha and beta manually or toggle their animation using the ui in the upper right corner
- control the camera rotation by dragging 
- control the camera zoom by mousewheel or pinch
